name: Autist
description: It's a meme token about autistic pepe. So it takes the very well known meme of an autistic pepe and uses him as a character on Hyperliquid. He has the hyperliquid logo on his head and on some of his outfits. This makes the meme unique in a sense as it's the only pepe meme that is currently available on Hyperliquid. There is a good chance it will keep being the only pepe meme on hyperliquid with auction prices going higher and higher.
